Appium locators:

- xpath: absolute & relative
* in selenium the xpath pattern is: 
//tagName[@attributeName='attributeValue']

* in Appium the xpath pattern is:
//className[@attributeName='attributeValue']


//android.widget.TextView[@text='Chrome']

- id:

-className:
- AndroidUIAutomator (android specific)
-AccessibilityId (mobile apps specific)

